data.name: label6.Text
data.value: This button will: - Refresh the Processed Demo List by checking what files are inside the final folder. - Check for new finished segments in the game. If one is found, it is moved to the work folder and an entry for it is then added to the Demo List

data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
The goal of this tool is to make handling segments' demos and saves easier and more organized for runners.
It attempts this by cataloging saves and demos from finished segment attempts by moving new ones into a work folder. From there, you can "process" segments you are satisfied with, which will rename them according to a customizable naming scheme and move them into the final folder.

data.name: label3.Text
data.value: To use this tool, you first set up 2 folders: a work folder and a final folder, then designate them in the Settings. You will also need to fill out other information in the Settings for the tool to operate correctly.
